lead_paragraph: World number 15 Gerina Piller was disappointed not to make full use of her extra length off the tee as the American slid to a 73 in the Ricoh Women's British Open first round on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Woburn Not Long Enough for World Number 15 Piller
